---
title: Glazed Chicken Breasts with Sheet Pan Roasted Veggies
description: A classic no fuss dinner for any night of the week! Chicken thighs get coated in thyme and balsamic glaze, then roasted with a medley of seasonal veggies to make a sheet pan dinner that will have everyone smiling!
